           SHORT="An X viewer for Microsoft chm files"

cat << EOF
xchm is an X viewer for Microsoft(R) chm files. It can show the content
tree if one is available, print pages, change font face and size,
remember bookmarks, display a searchable index, and search for words in
the current page and the whole book.
EOF
